Package org.osmdroid.views

This package contains all of the osmdroid views, including the base MapView, MapController, DefaultOverlayManager and all of the overlay structures.

Package org.osmdroid.views Description

This package contains all of the osmdroid views, including the base MapView, MapController, DefaultOverlayManager and all of the overlay structures. In general, if it can be seen by the user, it's probably in here.
